14.content: So how about Kim and her mother where having a nice relaxing day. Then they heard a loud noise in the garage, they rushed inside but get suck into a dimensional vortex created by Jim and Tim ?
14.title: Mother and daughter adventure

141.content:
Kim and her mother Ann where eating breakfast in the kitchen. Kim was dressed in a purple blouse and black mini skirt (with a purple lace bra, matching thong and black thigh high stockings). Ann was dress in a blue dress with her white lab coat ( with a red corset, matching thong and blue thigh high stockings). They where both relaxing, as neither of them had anything to do today.

Then suddenly there was aloud explosion coming the from thr garage. Ann was worried, why Kim rolled her eyes and cursed the tweebs. The redheaded mother and daughter raced into the garage to see if Jim and Tim was alright. Then they opened the door, all they saw was a giant swirling blue vortex. They where caught and quickly pulled into it.

Jim and Tim where off to a side, as they watched helplessly as both their mother and sister was pulled into the vortex.

" You know what this means." Said Jim.

" We have the run of the house." Said Tim, as the two high five each other.

Kim and Ann where spinning through the worm hole, neither knowing what was going to happen to them. Then soon there was a bright light and they fell onto the ground.

What kind of world do they find themselves on ?
141.title: yes

1411.content:
Ann and Kim slowly picked themselves up and looked around. They where surrounded by strange large blue plants. They looked down and saw the ground was a bright red, then they looked up and the sky was purple.

" Dweebs what do you do !" Shouted Kim, as she clenched her fists.

" Kim calm down." Said Ann, looking at her daughter.

" Why, because of them we're not on Earth anymore and who knows if we will ever get back." Said Kim, she felt anger and some fear.

" Kim, I sure your brother and already contacted both your father and Wade. It shouldn't be to long before they find us." Said Ann, as she hugged her daughter.

Kim sighed, " Fine, but once we're back. I'm going pound them into the ground." Said Kim, Ann sighed.
